variables.name: suspendAttemptCount
variables.comment: Total number of times that suspend was attempted

variables.name: failedSuspendCount
variables.comment: Total number of times that suspend attempt failed

variables.name: shortSuspendCount
variables.comment:
* Total number of times that a short suspend occurred. A successful suspend is considered a
   * short suspend if the suspend duration is less than suspend.short_suspend_threshold_millis

variables.name: suspendTimeMillis
variables.comment: Total time, in milliseconds, spent in suspend

variables.name: shortSuspendTimeMillis
variables.comment: Total time, in milliseconds, spent in short suspends

variables.name: suspendOverheadTimeMillis
variables.comment: Total time, in milliseconds, spent doing suspend/resume work for successful suspends

variables.name: failedSuspendOverheadTimeMillis
variables.comment: Total time, in milliseconds, spent doing suspend/resume work for failed suspends

variables.name: newBackoffCount
variables.comment:
* Total number of times the number of consecutive bad (short, failed) suspends
   * crossed suspend.backoff_threshold_count

variables.name: backoffContinueCount
variables.comment:
* Total number of times the number of consecutive bad (short, failed) suspends
   * exceeded suspend.backoff_threshold_count

variables.name: sleepTimeMillis
variables.comment: Total time, in milliseconds, that system has waited between suspend attempts
